---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BlogDisclaimer from '../components/BlogDisclaimer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Praveen Srinag Yellamaraju - AI Advisor and enterprise systems specialist.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <article class="prose">
          <h1>About Me</h1>
          
          <div class="intro-section">
            <img src="/images/praveen.jpg" alt="Praveen Srinag Yellamaraju" class="profile-image" />
            <div class="intro-text">
              <p class="lead">
                I'm an AI Advisor and enterprise systems specialist with 17+ years of experience 
                building intelligent, scalable solutions. In my current role, I perform architecture 
                and design responsibilities for AI systems.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h2>What I Do</h2>
          <p>
            In my role as an AI Advisor, I specialize in designing and implementing AI-powered systems 
            for enterprise environments. My responsibilities include architecting solutions for agentic AI, 
            multi-agent orchestration, RAG systems, and LLM-based applications using platforms like OpenAI, 
            Anthropic Claude, and Google ADK.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Currently, I'm building internal AI agents and tools that integrate with GitLab, Jira, 
            Confluence, ServiceNow, and various database systems. Through my work, I've designed and 
            architected production-ready solutions including automated code reviewers, change request creators, 
            and intelligent chatbots that enhance developer productivity and operational efficiency.
          </p>
          
          <h2>Knowledge Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            I'm passionate about education and community contribution. I've delivered over 17 sessions 
            on AI-related topics and conducted multiple workshops on Prompt Engineering, AI Agents, 
            and Agentic AI design. Teaching helps me refine my understanding and contribute to the 
            broader AI community.
          </p>
          
          <h2>Background</h2>
          <p>
            My journey spans full-stack development, cloud architecture, and now AI/ML systems. 
            I hold a Post Graduate Diploma in Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence from 
            NIT Warangal, along with certifications in AWS Solution Architecture, TOGAF Enterprise 
            Architecture, and Docker.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            I've worked with leading organizations including Fiserv, CGI, and Capgemini, where I've 
            led cloud migrations, designed microservices architectures, and implemented DevOps practices 
            that significantly improved system reliability and deployment efficiency.
          </p>
          
          <h2>This Website</h2>
          <p>
            I write about AI/ML, agentic systems, prompt engineering, enterprise architecture, and 
            the practical challenges of implementing AI in production environments. My goal is to 
            share what I learn, document patterns that work, and contribute to conversations about 
            responsible AI development.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            If you're working on similar challenges or want to discuss AI architecture, feel free to 
            <a href="/contact">reach out</a>. I'm always interested in connecting with fellow 
            practitioners and learning from different perspectives.
          </p>
          
          <div class="cta-section">
            <h3>Let's Connect</h3>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
              <a href="/contact" class="primary-button">Get in Touch</a>
              <a href="/resume" class="secondary-button">View Resume</a>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/praveensrinagy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="secondary-button">
                LinkedIn Profile
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="disclaimer-section">
            <BlogDisclaimer type="full" />
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }
  
  .prose {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .intro-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: start;
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .profile-image {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-section h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .disclaimer-section {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .primary-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .primary-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
  }
  
  .secondary-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .secondary-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .profile-image {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
  }
</style>
